WEBVTT

00:00:43.030 --> 00:00:50.970
[Sharp Blade in the Snow]

00:00:51.010 --> 00:00:54.070
[Episode 14]

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:06.000
Stop right there.

00:01:13.760 --> 00:01:15.289
What happened to your hand?

00:01:16.520 --> 00:01:17.780
I was careless just now

00:01:18.280 --> 00:01:19.880
and hit it on the stone steps.

00:01:21.120 --> 00:01:22.320
You're a grown man now

00:01:22.560 --> 00:01:24.240
yet still so reckless.

00:01:25.039 --> 00:01:26.640
You can't even walk properly.

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:29.520
How could you possibly
serve as the Imperial Consort?

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:31.580
You're so timid in front of the Queen,

00:01:31.880 --> 00:01:33.940
afraid to even touch her fingertips.

00:01:34.080 --> 00:01:35.680
How will you ever please her?

00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:37.400
If this continues,

00:01:37.400 --> 00:01:38.400
sooner or later those male concubines

00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:39.680
will walk all over you.

00:01:39.920 --> 00:01:40.850
Enough, Mother!

00:01:41.920 --> 00:01:43.520
What more do you want me to do?

00:01:44.920 --> 00:01:45.960
Do you want me to be like

00:01:45.960 --> 00:01:46.840
Xiao Ze,

00:01:47.680 --> 00:01:49.240
flaunting myself all day

00:01:49.240 --> 00:01:50.700
with seductive behavior?

00:01:51.160 --> 00:01:52.520
Isn't my current state

00:01:52.960 --> 00:01:54.240
miserable enough?

00:01:54.759 --> 00:01:56.759
How much more
do you want me to debase myself?

00:01:56.759 --> 00:01:57.560
You...

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:04.360
Rest well.

00:02:05.760 --> 00:02:07.040
Keep the wound dry

00:02:07.560 --> 00:02:08.620
to avoid scarring.

00:02:22.280 --> 00:02:23.640
I am an envoy from Xiqi.

00:02:23.880 --> 00:02:25.340
Greetings, Your Majesty.

00:02:26.640 --> 00:02:28.840
Xiqi has been gaining momentum lately.

00:02:28.880 --> 00:02:30.480
You've already conquered two cities.

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:31.880
Envoy, what brings you

00:02:32.240 --> 00:02:33.570
to Mocheng so suddenly?

00:02:34.040 --> 00:02:35.280
Your Majesty, you're still young

00:02:35.280 --> 00:02:36.680
and may not be aware.

00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:39.360
Prime Minister Bai should still remember

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:42.420
the agreement between Xiqi and Mocheng
from years ago.

00:02:47.800 --> 00:02:50.040
I just had a few words
of argument with her

00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:52.640
and now she really wants
to marry me off to Xiqi.

00:02:52.640 --> 00:02:53.680
I've heard that the young master of Xiqi

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:55.960
has worn a mask
since childhood due to illness.

00:02:55.960 --> 00:02:57.800
No one has ever seen his face.

00:02:58.000 --> 00:02:59.440
He must be ugly.

00:02:59.960 --> 00:03:01.920
This isn't just a political marriage.

00:03:01.920 --> 00:03:04.160
This is clearly asking for my life.

00:03:05.440 --> 00:03:06.440
Aunt.

00:03:08.640 --> 00:03:11.080
I've heard that the personality
of the young master of Xiqi

00:03:11.080 --> 00:03:13.040
is even more terrifying.

00:03:13.560 --> 00:03:15.000
To establish military authority,

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:17.320
he often punishes people
for minor offenses

00:03:17.320 --> 00:03:18.850
by cutting off their limbs.

00:03:19.520 --> 00:03:21.360
Now I'm confined to the mansion,

00:03:21.920 --> 00:03:23.560
while Li holds all the power.

00:03:25.200 --> 00:03:27.560
Even if I want to help you refuse,

00:03:28.200 --> 00:03:29.680
she won't listen to me.

00:03:30.800 --> 00:03:31.600
Aunt.

00:03:32.280 --> 00:03:33.600
Could it be that I truly have no choice

00:03:33.600 --> 00:03:35.200
but to be manipulated by her?

00:03:35.720 --> 00:03:36.720
In a few days,

00:03:36.960 --> 00:03:38.640
the Xiqi delegation will arrive,

00:03:38.640 --> 00:03:40.840
and there will be no turning back.

00:03:41.600 --> 00:03:42.640
Li's position

00:03:42.800 --> 00:03:44.000
is not yet secure.

00:03:44.400 --> 00:03:45.600
The marriage alliance

00:03:45.600 --> 00:03:47.280
is for border stability.

00:03:47.920 --> 00:03:49.960
The young master of Xiqi
is a brilliant talent

00:03:49.960 --> 00:03:51.280
who has never lost a battle.

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:53.480
In recent years, he has achieved
numerous military victories

00:03:53.480 --> 00:03:55.000
and has already become Mocheng's

00:03:55.000 --> 00:03:56.360
greatest threat.

00:03:57.160 --> 00:03:58.960
You must not lose your manners

00:03:58.960 --> 00:04:00.960
or do anything outrageous.

00:04:01.800 --> 00:04:04.200
A failed marriage alliance
is the least of our concerns.

00:04:04.200 --> 00:04:06.800
If it gives them an excuse to march on us,

00:04:07.400 --> 00:04:09.530
that's where the real trouble begins.

00:04:13.880 --> 00:04:15.840
I will certainly behave well

00:04:17.440 --> 00:04:19.000
and make my dear sister

00:04:19.839 --> 00:04:21.040
proud.

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:25.640
Good child.

00:04:31.880 --> 00:04:32.680
Feng Li,

00:04:33.240 --> 00:04:36.370
if you're heartless,
don't blame me for being ruthless.

00:04:36.600 --> 00:04:37.840
My wedding day

00:04:37.840 --> 00:04:39.440
will be the day of your death.

00:04:52.640 --> 00:04:54.760
You've delivered yourself right to me.

00:04:54.760 --> 00:04:56.320
You just started serving that girl

00:04:56.320 --> 00:04:58.250
and now you dare to come for my life.

00:04:58.320 --> 00:05:01.040
Slicing you into a thousand pieces
would not be too cruel.

00:05:01.040 --> 00:05:02.160
I want to see

00:05:02.320 --> 00:05:03.800
how she'll save you this time.

00:05:03.800 --> 00:05:04.730
For Her Majesty,

00:05:05.120 --> 00:05:06.360
I am willing to do anything.

00:05:06.360 --> 00:05:07.800
When we get to my palace,

00:05:08.080 --> 00:05:09.040
you'd better still be

00:05:09.040 --> 00:05:10.330
as defiant as you are now.

00:05:10.330 --> 00:05:14.190
[Fengling Hall]

00:05:16.160 --> 00:05:17.040
Look,

00:05:17.360 --> 00:05:19.020
what nice little tool is this?

00:05:20.080 --> 00:05:21.360
Tell me,

00:05:22.200 --> 00:05:23.600
which finger should I

00:05:23.600 --> 00:05:25.040
start with?

00:05:28.040 --> 00:05:28.920
Today,

00:05:29.400 --> 00:05:30.360
I will tear you, the star

00:05:30.360 --> 00:05:32.000
from Feng Li's heart.

00:05:41.920 --> 00:05:43.720
Are you done with this nonsense?

00:05:44.960 --> 00:05:46.420
Greetings, Your Majesty.

00:05:46.720 --> 00:05:48.520
He openly attempted to assassinate me.

00:05:48.520 --> 00:05:50.320
For such a deranged person,

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:52.600
why shouldn't I impose punishment?

00:05:52.960 --> 00:05:54.360
You claim he attempted assassination,

00:05:54.360 --> 00:05:55.480
but do you have evidence?

00:05:55.480 --> 00:05:56.520
I am the evidence.

00:05:57.200 --> 00:05:58.000
I did not.

00:05:58.240 --> 00:05:59.040
I merely

00:05:59.040 --> 00:06:00.920
met Princess Ling in the corridor.

00:06:00.920 --> 00:06:01.600
I only

00:06:01.920 --> 00:06:03.450
spoke well of Your Majesty.

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:05.640
She became angry from embarrassment

00:06:05.640 --> 00:06:07.160
and then had me brought here.

00:06:07.160 --> 00:06:08.000
What?

00:06:08.680 --> 00:06:10.120
You just insisted

00:06:10.120 --> 00:06:11.720
that you came to kill me because of her.

00:06:11.720 --> 00:06:12.840
Nonsense!

00:06:17.560 --> 00:06:18.960
If I wanted to kill you,

00:06:18.960 --> 00:06:21.020
why would I need someone else to do it?

00:06:21.680 --> 00:06:23.520
Everyone here today witnessed

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:25.520
that you kidnapped my man,

00:06:25.960 --> 00:06:27.420
tortured him recklessly,

00:06:27.720 --> 00:06:29.240
and by law should be executed.

00:06:29.240 --> 00:06:31.440
Considering you'll be sent to Xiqi
for a political marriage in a few days,

00:06:31.440 --> 00:06:32.840
I'll spare you this time.

00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:39.360
If I hear more

00:06:39.360 --> 00:06:41.159
of your gossiping rumors again,

00:06:41.560 --> 00:06:42.920
that mouth of yours

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:45.000
won't be needed anymore!

00:06:45.120 --> 00:06:46.280
From today on,

00:06:46.280 --> 00:06:47.880
you are confined here,

00:06:48.040 --> 00:06:49.680
and no one may enter or leave.

00:07:00.520 --> 00:07:02.160
Violators will be executed.

00:07:03.240 --> 00:07:04.300
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:07:06.680 --> 00:07:07.720
Feng Li!

00:07:12.680 --> 00:07:13.480
Your Majesty.

00:07:16.200 --> 00:07:17.000
Your Majesty.

00:07:18.320 --> 00:07:19.120
Your Majesty!

00:07:22.240 --> 00:07:22.970
Why is it you?

00:07:23.400 --> 00:07:24.600
Where is Her Majesty?

00:07:26.200 --> 00:07:26.930
Don't tell me

00:07:27.360 --> 00:07:28.620
you expect Her Majesty

00:07:28.640 --> 00:07:29.840
to serve you herself.

00:07:30.520 --> 00:07:31.850
Who do you think you are?

00:07:32.159 --> 00:07:33.840
How dare you treat me
with such disrespect?

00:07:33.840 --> 00:07:34.720
Let me tell you,

00:07:35.200 --> 00:07:37.400
I'm now Her Majesty's favorite person.

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:40.080
Your Majesty.

00:07:41.080 --> 00:07:43.960
Her Majesty ordered me to serve you,

00:07:44.280 --> 00:07:45.800
her precious slave.

00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:49.800
It depends on your performance.

00:07:50.040 --> 00:07:51.480
If you serve me well,

00:07:52.040 --> 00:07:53.480
I'll naturally put in

00:07:54.240 --> 00:07:56.240
a good word for you with Her Majesty.

00:07:57.040 --> 00:07:58.320
What are you standing there for?

00:07:58.320 --> 00:07:59.400
Get me some water.

00:07:59.400 --> 00:08:01.460
Are you trying to let me die of thirst?

00:08:10.400 --> 00:08:11.520
Where's my water?

00:08:19.560 --> 00:08:21.400
How dare you! What are you doing?

00:08:21.960 --> 00:08:23.760
I'll report this to Her Majesty!

00:08:24.440 --> 00:08:25.400
So thirsty?

00:08:25.760 --> 00:08:26.320
Right.

00:08:26.920 --> 00:08:28.280
Her Majesty specifically instructed me

00:08:28.280 --> 00:08:29.680
to take good care of you.

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:30.640
So I'll

00:08:31.160 --> 00:08:32.640
feed you the water myself.

00:08:37.440 --> 00:08:38.240
You...

00:08:39.039 --> 00:08:39.840
No!

00:08:40.880 --> 00:08:41.640
Help!

00:08:43.120 --> 00:08:44.280
Let me go!

00:09:26.960 --> 00:09:28.880
Today's tribute tea has pine fragrance.

00:09:28.880 --> 00:09:31.010
Would you like to try it, Your Majesty?

00:09:31.560 --> 00:09:33.090
What happened to your hand?

00:09:36.240 --> 00:09:37.040
The other day,

00:09:37.320 --> 00:09:40.250
I wanted to carve
a jade seal for Your Majesty myself.

00:09:40.600 --> 00:09:42.040
The carving knife was sharp.

00:09:42.040 --> 00:09:44.040
I was careless and cut myself.

00:09:55.200 --> 00:09:56.200
Does it hurt?

00:09:58.360 --> 00:09:59.290
It doesn't hurt.

00:09:59.800 --> 00:10:01.000
It's already healed.

00:10:02.600 --> 00:10:04.000
You're always like this.

00:10:05.840 --> 00:10:07.000
You get injured

00:10:07.320 --> 00:10:08.780
and never tell me about it.

00:10:11.080 --> 00:10:12.000
That day,

00:10:12.560 --> 00:10:14.400
I was a bit harsh with you.

00:10:15.520 --> 00:10:17.050
Are you still upset with me?

00:10:17.760 --> 00:10:19.200
How could I be upset with you?

00:10:19.200 --> 00:10:20.600
I was overly concerned.

00:10:21.560 --> 00:10:23.490
There must be some special reason.

00:10:23.560 --> 00:10:26.160
I should have trusted
Your Majesty's resolve.

00:10:31.720 --> 00:10:33.580
You're always so understanding.

00:10:44.640 --> 00:10:47.170
Actually, he resembles
someone from my past.

00:11:03.080 --> 00:11:03.880
Is...

00:11:04.960 --> 00:11:06.680
Is he the boy you once mentioned

00:11:06.680 --> 00:11:07.560
who was with you in the wasteland

00:11:07.560 --> 00:11:09.360
and survived together with you?

00:11:11.200 --> 00:11:12.040
Yes.

00:11:12.680 --> 00:11:13.880
Fate is full of irony.

00:11:14.840 --> 00:11:17.500
I never expected to meet
him again in the palace.

00:11:19.240 --> 00:11:20.370
Then, Your Majesty,

00:11:20.840 --> 00:11:23.370
how do you plan
to arrange for this old friend?

00:11:34.760 --> 00:11:37.240
I'll have to think about it carefully.

00:12:02.280 --> 00:12:03.140
Your Highness.

00:12:05.000 --> 00:12:07.730
This is by order
of the Princess Royal of Mocheng.

00:12:09.360 --> 00:12:10.160
This medicine

00:12:10.520 --> 00:12:12.920
should be delivered
to the Demon Lord by me.

00:12:17.840 --> 00:12:18.700
Your Highness!

00:12:19.880 --> 00:12:20.740
Your Highness.

00:12:24.280 --> 00:12:25.410
Something's wrong.

00:12:25.560 --> 00:12:27.040
Your Highness's pulse doesnâ€™t feel right.

00:12:27.040 --> 00:12:28.800
No wonder the Queen of Mocheng
takes daily tonics

00:12:28.800 --> 00:12:30.000
laced with poison,

00:12:30.040 --> 00:12:31.760
yet shows no signs of poisoning.

00:12:31.760 --> 00:12:32.620
So those tonics

00:12:33.280 --> 00:12:35.080
were all taken by Your Highness.

00:12:36.680 --> 00:12:38.160
This poison specifically targets the heart

00:12:38.160 --> 00:12:39.920
and is nearly impossible to counter.

00:12:39.920 --> 00:12:41.980
Your Highness, why would you do this?

00:12:44.160 --> 00:12:45.560
I have my own plans.

00:12:46.160 --> 00:12:47.890
You need not concern yourself.

00:12:49.680 --> 00:12:50.720
Feng Li's life

00:12:51.600 --> 00:12:52.920
is mine alone to take.

00:12:58.360 --> 00:12:59.220
Your Highness!

00:13:03.800 --> 00:13:05.530
There's been a change of plans.

00:13:05.560 --> 00:13:06.620
Starting tonight,

00:13:07.280 --> 00:13:09.480
you will enter the palace
as a court lady

00:13:09.520 --> 00:13:12.040
and seize the opportunity
to assassinate the Queen of Mocheng.

00:13:12.040 --> 00:13:12.760
Be quick.

00:13:13.080 --> 00:13:13.880
Yes.

00:13:32.920 --> 00:13:34.780
It's late at night with heavy dew.

00:13:35.040 --> 00:13:35.760
Court lady,

00:13:36.200 --> 00:13:38.000
where are you going to serve now?

00:13:38.520 --> 00:13:39.960
I am a court lady in the palace

00:13:39.960 --> 00:13:41.560
of the newly appointed Queen.

00:13:41.560 --> 00:13:44.220
I'm on my way
to serve the Queen at Fengxi Palace.

00:13:48.680 --> 00:13:49.880
Wandering around

00:13:50.160 --> 00:13:51.560
is against the rules.

00:13:52.200 --> 00:13:53.280
Fengxi Palace?

00:13:55.440 --> 00:13:58.320
Fengxi Palace is not exactly
a place of good fortune.

00:13:58.320 --> 00:13:59.240
I advise you

00:13:59.760 --> 00:14:01.480
not to set foot in that place.

00:14:01.760 --> 00:14:02.890
I came here on orders

00:14:03.280 --> 00:14:05.680
and have no intention
of giving up halfway.

00:14:09.160 --> 00:14:09.960
Ruo!

00:14:12.280 --> 00:14:13.880
Your Highness has good eyes.

00:14:31.600 --> 00:14:33.120
Among General Lu's subordinates,

00:14:33.120 --> 00:14:35.050
you're the only one who can match me

00:14:35.320 --> 00:14:36.640
for a few moves, Ruo.

00:14:40.800 --> 00:14:43.060
Unfortunately, Your Highness is unwell

00:14:43.320 --> 00:14:44.600
and may not be my match.

00:14:44.960 --> 00:14:47.090
The Xiqi delegation arrives in 3 days.

00:14:47.480 --> 00:14:49.440
Once the marriage alliance is formed,

00:14:49.440 --> 00:14:51.760
Dongli will have little chance
to restore its kingdom.

00:14:51.760 --> 00:14:53.000
I came here

00:14:53.040 --> 00:14:54.760
to assist Your Highness

00:14:55.280 --> 00:14:57.340
in killing the Demon Lord of Mocheng.

00:14:58.480 --> 00:14:59.520
Feng Li's life

00:15:00.560 --> 00:15:01.800
is mine alone to take.

00:15:02.480 --> 00:15:04.000
When and how to kill her

00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:07.130
is not for any of you to interfere with.

00:15:13.720 --> 00:15:14.580
Your Highness,

00:15:15.200 --> 00:15:17.260
you can barely control your own life,

00:15:17.600 --> 00:15:19.560
how can you control others'?

00:15:21.920 --> 00:15:24.180
If you still acknowledge me as your lord,

00:15:24.840 --> 00:15:25.640
get out now.

00:15:33.840 --> 00:15:34.880
This Yun Zhan

00:15:35.480 --> 00:15:36.640
is truly despicable.